




# ViewComponent

```jsx
const fileName = "_OPERATION/PRIVATE/DATACORE/8 FitnessExplorer/D.q.fitnessexplorer.component.md"

const { FrontSvg } = await dc.require(
  dc.headerLink(fileName, "FrontSvg")
);
const { BackSvg } = await dc.require(
  dc.headerLink(fileName, "BackSvg")
);
const { FrontSystemSvg } = await dc.require(
  dc.headerLink(fileName, "FrontSystemSvg")
);
const { FrontOrgansSvg } = await dc.require(
  dc.headerLink(fileName, "FrontOrgansSvg")
);
const { useState, useEffect, useRef } = dc;

/**
 * Optional: A reusable HoverGroup component that creates a full hit area.
 */
function HoverGroup({ onClick, children, style, ...rest }) {
  const groupRef = useRef(null);
  const [bbox, setBbox] = useState(null);

  useEffect(() => {
    if (groupRef.current) {
      setBbox(groupRef.current.getBBox());
    }
  }, [children]);

	

  return (
    <g
      ref={groupRef}
      onClick={onClick}
      className="hover-group"
      style={{ cursor: "pointer", ...style }}
      {...rest}
    >
      {bbox && (
        <rect
          x={bbox.x}
          y={bbox.y}
          width={bbox.width}
          height={bbox.height}
          fill="transparent"
          style={{ pointerEvents: "all" }}
        />
      )}
      {children}
    </g>
  );
}

function FitnessView({ onFileSelect, file }) {
  const [showFront, setShowFront] = useState(true);
  const [isDarkMode, setIsDarkMode] = useState(true);
  // frontViewIndex: 0 = FrontSvg, 1 = FrontSystemSvg, 2 = FrontOrgansSvg
  const [frontViewIndex, setFrontViewIndex] = useState(0);
  const [hoveredGroup, setHoveredGroup] = useState(null);
  const [scale, setScale] = useState(0.5);
  const [translateX, setTranslateX] = useState(0);
  const containerRef = useRef(null);

  // When the "file" prop is provided (when coming back from View),
  // parse it to restore the correct front view.
  useEffect(() => {
    if (file) {
      const lowerFile = file.toLowerCase();
      if (lowerFile.includes("organs")) {
        setFrontViewIndex(2);
      } else if (lowerFile.includes("system")) {
        setFrontViewIndex(1);
      } else {
        setFrontViewIndex(0);
      }
    }
  }, [file]);


/// Update scale and translation based on container width.
  useEffect(() => {
    const updateScaleAndTranslate = () => {
      if (containerRef.current) {
        const containerWidth = containerRef.current.clientWidth;
        const newScale = containerWidth / 555; // adjust based on your base width
        const clampedScale = Math.max(0.3, Math.min(newScale, 1));
        setScale(clampedScale);
        const baseSvgWidth = 465; // the SVG's viewBox width
        const additionalOffset = 20; // tweak to center properly
        const tx =
          containerWidth / (2 * clampedScale) - baseSvgWidth / 2 + additionalOffset;
        setTranslateX(tx);
      }
    };

    updateScaleAndTranslate();
    let observer;
    if (typeof ResizeObserver !== "undefined") {
      observer = new ResizeObserver(updateScaleAndTranslate);
      if (containerRef.current) observer.observe(containerRef.current);
    } else {
      window.addEventListener("resize", updateScaleAndTranslate);
    }
    return () => {
      if (observer && containerRef.current) {
        observer.unobserve(containerRef.current);
      } else {
        window.removeEventListener("resize", updateScaleAndTranslate);
      }
    };
  }, []);

  // ... (rest of your FitnessView code remains unchanged)
  
  // Choose the front component based on frontViewIndex.
  let FrontComponent;
  if (frontViewIndex === 0) {
    FrontComponent = FrontSvg;
  } else if (frontViewIndex === 1) {
    FrontComponent = FrontSystemSvg;
  } else if (frontViewIndex === 2) {
    FrontComponent = FrontOrgansSvg;
  }

  return (
    <div ref={containerRef} style={{ padding: "10px", backgroundColor: isDarkMode ? "#000" : "#fff", color: isDarkMode ? "#fff" : "#000", minHeight: "666vh" }}>
      {/* Header Section */}
      <div style={{ display: "flex", justifyContent: "space-between", alignItems: "center", marginBottom: "10px", borderBottom: "1px solid #888", paddingBottom: "8px" }}>
        <div>
          <button onClick={() => setIsDarkMode(prev => !prev)}>
            {isDarkMode ? "Switch to Light Mode" : "Switch to Dark Mode"}
          </button>
          {/* Disable the "Show Back" button when not in the default front view */}
          <button onClick={() => setShowFront(prev => !prev)} disabled={showFront && frontViewIndex !== 0}>
            {showFront ? "Show Back" : "Show Front"}
          </button>
        </div>
        {showFront && (
          <div style={{ display: "flex", alignItems: "center", gap: "8px" }}>
            <span>Front</span>
            <input
              type="range"
              min="0"
              max="2"
              step="1"
              value={frontViewIndex}
              onChange={(e) => setFrontViewIndex(Number(e.target.value))}
              style={{ width: "150px" }}
            />
            <span>
              {frontViewIndex === 0
                ? "SVG"
                : frontViewIndex === 1
                ? "System"
                : "Organs"}
            </span>
          </div>
        )}
      </div>
      <div style={{ width: "66vw" }}>
        {showFront ? (
          <FrontComponent
            mode={isDarkMode ? "dark" : "light"}
            onGroupClick={onFileSelect}
            hoveredGroup={hoveredGroup}
            setHoveredGroup={setHoveredGroup}
            scale={scale}
            translateX={translateX}
          />
        ) : (
          <BackSvg
            mode={isDarkMode ? "dark" : "light"}
            onGroupClick={onFileSelect}
            hoveredGroup={hoveredGroup}
            setHoveredGroup={setHoveredGroup}
            scale={scale}
            translateX={translateX}
          />
        )}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}

return { FitnessView };

```
